      <title>更多美国人怀疑他们的汽车和住房贷款能否获得批准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/more-americans-doubt-they-ll-get-approved-for-auto-home-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约联邦储备银行进行的一项调查显示，美国人越来越怀疑他们能否获得购买汽车的贷款或抵押贷款再融资的批准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/more-americans-doubt-they-ll-get-approved-for-auto-home-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 18:34:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
